summary: Skyrim INI Tweaker is an application to assist you in tweaking your Skyrim.ini and SkyrimPrefs.ini file.
descriptionHtml:
[size=4]I introduce to you, Skyrim INI Tweaker![/size]
If you like this then please visit my community at: [url=http://pyronet.tv]PyroNet.TV[/url]

Microsoft .NET Framework 4 minimum [color=red][b]required[/b][/color], get it here:
[url=http://www.microsoft.com/download/en/details.aspx?id=17851]http://www.microsoft.com/download/en/details.aspx?id=17851[/url]

[size=3][b]I would like some help in describing what each setting does so anyone with any advice on telling me which setting does what (e.g. how it changes Skyrim), I would be greatly appreciative and I will add you to the credits.[/b][/size]

Source code is availabie here: http://code.google.com/p/skyrim-ini-tweaker/
author: NotoriousPyro

files.name: initweaker_046
files.changelogHtml: Auto backup creation on startup (Skyrim.ini.backup and SkyrimPrefs.ini.backup)
